{"about_the_game":"Embark on an epic adventure through treacherous caves, solving intricate puzzles, and battling fearsome enemies in <strong>Abyssal Descent</strong>. Journey from the depths of underground caves, through the underworld, and into the mysterious Hollow Earth Oasis and beyond as you search to find your place in the afterlife. With captivating exploration, strategic combat, and charming playable characters, this thrilling platformer delivers an exciting blend of action, puzzles, and discovery. Optional local co-op allows for you to bring a friend with you on this adventure, and the procedural generation means no two playthroughs will be the same. Are you ready to take the plunge into the abyss?<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Traverse diverse, procedurally generated underground caves, underworld, Hollow Earth, and more<br></li><li> Solve challenging puzzles and unlock hidden secrets... in the dark.<br></li><li> Engage in thrilling combat against a variety of enemies.<br></li><li> Purchase new gear, unlock new abilities, and harness ancient relics.<br></li><li> Optional local co-op to bring a friend on this adventure of a lifetime.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717722705","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506740/page.bg.jpg?t=1717722705","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506740/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1717722705","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506740/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1717722705","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descript